publisher			3Division							
publish_time	 2016年3月21日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Air Missions: HIND is action combat flight simulator based on the Russian Mi-24 Hind assault helicopter, also known as the "Flying Tank". Equip the weapon of your choice! - UPK 23 machineguns, GUV gunpods, FAB bombs, and variety of missiles. Use those weapons to tear up the sky in single player and multiplayer modes.Three control modes for casual and experienced playersOver fifteen missions based on fictional conflicts;Three different battlefields - Central Asia, Eastern Europe, and the Barents SeaSingleplayer and Multiplayer mode, including Campaign missions, Deathmatch, Instant Action, and Co-operative missionsAAM, MCLOS, SACLOS, S-5, S-8, S-13, S-24 - Use those to destroy the enemy!						
